trans-unit.source: Represents a number elements found in a <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken"></xref> which represent security tokens.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et tall elementer funnet i en <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.RequestSecurityToken"> </xref> som representerer sikkerhetstokener.

trans-unit.source: This class is not thread-safe.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er ikke sikker.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement"></xref> class by using a <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityToken"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av en <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityToken"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: When this constructor is used, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.GetIdentities%2A> method is not supported by the new instance unless the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.CreateSubject%2A> method is overridden.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker denne konstruktøren, den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.GetIdentities%2A>metoden støttes ikke av den nye forekomsten med mindre den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.CreateSubject%2A>metoden overstyres.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.CreateSubject%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.GetIdentities%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the `securityToken` parameter is an instance of <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.GenericXmlSecurityToken> then the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.SecurityTokenXml%2A> property is set to the value of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.GenericXmlSecurityToken.TokenXml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `securityToken` parameter er en forekomst av <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.GenericXmlSecurityToken>vil <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.SecurityTokenXml%2A>egenskapen er satt til verdien for den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.GenericXmlSecurityToken.TokenXml%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.GenericXmlSecurityToken.TokenXml%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenElement.SecurityTokenXml%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.GenericXmlSecurityToken>
